audioContentItems.fileTranscript: Thank you for calling Barnes and Noble. My name is (Your Name). How can I help you?
Hi. I placed an order and wanted to know the status. I should have received my order by now. I really need the books to give them as a gift next week.
I'm sorry you haven't received your order. I would be happy to check the status of your order. Can I have your order number, please?
My order number is 4 1 3 6 3 3 3 9 3 0.
Thank you. One moment while I locate your order.
No problem. I appreciate it.
Can I have you verify your email address, please?
Sure. My email address is anita napp at gmail.com.
Great, thanks! What is your shipping address, please?
My address is 5 7 2 Angel Place, Sunny, California 9 0 2 1 0.
Thank you. Just a moment please, while I research your order.
Thank you for your patience. I can see your order shipped on January 17th and was expected to be delivered by January 24th. One moment while I review the tracking details.
Okay, thanks. I appreciate your help.
Thank you for your patience. I've checked the tracking, and I can see that is was delivered on January 24th. Have you checked your mailbox and all of the doors?
Yes. I checked everywhere, and I still can't find the package.
I'm going to consider your order lost in transit. Give me a moment while I check the available options.
Sure.
Great news! I have the items in stock, and can have your order replaced free of charge. Would you like me to replace them?
Yes, I want them replaced. I need them for a gift next week.
Absolutely! Due to the inconvenience, I will upgrade the shipping level as well.
Ok, thanks! That would be great, and will help so much!
Of course. It's my pleasure since you didn't receive them.
Are there any changes to the delivery address that we need to make?
No, it will go to the same address, but can you add apartment B onto the shipping address?
Yes, I can update the address to include your apartment number.
The expected delivery date for your order would be on Friday, February 3rd.
Ok, sounds good. That should be before the party.
You'll receive an email confirming the order shortly. You will also receive a shipping confirmation email when the order ships, which includes tracking information.
Your new order number is 6180000649. I will also email you a return label in case you receive the original and the replacement.
I just received the first email. Thank you.
You're welcome. Is there anything else I can assist you with?
No, that's it. Thanks!
Thank you! Have a great day, and thanks for calling Barnes and Noble.

settings.text:
This simulation will give you practice in handling advanced call type. You can go through this as many times as desired until you feel confident in the navigation and call flow.
The test version of the advanced simulation will provide you with no prompts. You will need to create your own words instead of reading scripting. Have your audio and microphone ready. You must complete the test version to receive credit for completion of this simulation. Let's get started.
Click into the 'Order Number' field and type, '4136333930.' Then press 'Enter.'
Click into the 'Search' field and type, 'Lost.' Then press 'Enter.'
Click into the 'Address 2' field and type, 'Apt B.' Then press 'Enter.'
Click into the 'Issue' field and type, 'Customer checking on order status.' Then press 'Enter.'
Click into the 'Resolution' field and type, 'Order is late. PDD 01/24. Issued RO and advised PDD 02/03 and email confirms will be sent. Issued a return label. RO number.' Then press 'Enter.'
